          </div>
          <div class="social-track-wrapper">
            <div class="social-track" id="socialTrack">
              {igPosts.map(post => (
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/cozy_aura_candle/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-post" aria-label="View Instagram post">
                  <div class="social-post-img" id={`ig-post-${post.id}`} style={`background:${post.gradient};display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;`}>
                    <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--taupe)" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"/></svg>
                  </div>

                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="home-section home-testimonials">
      <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center;justify-content:center;">
        <h2>What Our <em>Customers</em> Say</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-stars">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <p>"The sandalwood candle is absolutely divine. It fills the entire room with a warm, grounding scent that lasts for hours. My new favourite ritual."</p>
          <span class="testimonial-author">— Ananya R.</span>
        </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-stars">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p>"Beautifully packaged and the burn time is incredible. You can tell real care goes into every candle. Already ordered three more as gifts."</p>
            <span class="testimonial-author">— Vikram S.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-stars">
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--gold)" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--gold)" stroke-width="1"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p>"The lavender candle is my bedtime essential. Clean burn, no black soot, and the fragrance is perfectly balanced — not overpowering."</p>
            <span class="testimonial-author">— Priya M.</span>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="shop" class={initialPage === 'shop' ? 'active' : ''}>
    <div style="max-width:1300px; margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>The <em>Collection</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="shop-controls" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <div class="filter-bar" id="categoryFilters" style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;"></div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; flex: 1; justify-content: flex-end; max-width: 600px;">
          <div style="position: relative; display: flex; border: 1px solid var(--sand); background: white; padding: 2px; width: 100%; max-width: 320px;">
            <input type="text" id="shopSearchInput" placeholder="Search candles..." style="border: none; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.85rem; outline: none; flex: 1; background: transparent;" oninput="window.triggerSearch()">
            <button class="btn-primary" onclick="window.triggerSearch()" style="padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem; font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; border: none; cursor: pointer;">Search</button>
          </div>
          <label for="shopSortSelect" class="sr-only">Sort by</label>
          <select id="shopSortSelect" onchange="window.triggerSearch()" style="border: 1px solid var(--sand); background: white; padding: 0.7rem 1.2rem; font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.8rem; outline: none; cursor: pointer; color: var(--stone); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;">
            <option value="default">Sort By: Featured</option>
            <option value="name-asc">Alphabetical: A-Z</option>
            <option value="name-desc">Alphabetical: Z-A</option>
            <option value="price-asc">Price: Low to High</option>
            <option value="price-desc">Price: High to Low</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid" id="productsGrid">{productsGridHtml ? <fragment set:html={productsGridHtml} /> : ''}</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="cartPage" class={initialPage === 'cartPage' ? 'active' : ''}>
    <div class="cart-inner">
      <div class="cart-left">
        <h2>Your <em>Order</em></h2>
        <div class="order-items-container" id="orderItemsContainer"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="checkout-summary" style="position: sticky; top: 7rem;">
